CalculateField Road_Risk_Mar2011 SCORE road VB "Dim road
road = 0
If [Quick_ID] = PHR Then
road = 1.4
Elseif [Quick_ID] = PMR Then
road = 1.8
Elseif [Quick_ID] = PLR or [Quick_ID] = SHR Then
road = 2.2
Elseif [Quick_ID] = SMR Then
road = 3.2
Elseif [Quick_ID] = SLR Then
road = 4.0
Else
road = 0
End If"
